title: Lyn Woodward (Kelley Blue Book)
description:
Lyn Woodward is an automotive journalist at Kelley Blue Book and on the KBB YouTube Channel. She recently competed the Rebelle Rally, the first women’s off-road navigation rally in the United States. Find her work here:

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCj9yUGuMVVdm2DqyvJPUeUQ

https://www.rebellerally.com/info/

 

Watch the show! https://youtu.be/IFoOpM2uLS0

Follow us!

T: @thesmokingtire @zackklapman 

IG: @thesmokingtire @fakezackklapman @lyn_woodward
